<div class="hero min-h-[70vh]">
  <div class="hero-content text-center">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <section class="text-lg [&>*]:mt-8">
        <p>
          Make quizzes, take quizzes, manage quiz sessions, and keep track of the results.
        </p>
        <p>
          Make quizzes with customized questions, or generate random math questions for practice (e.g. '2 + 3 = ?').
        </p>
        <p>
          Great for teachers who want to make quizzes for their students, or for anyone who wants to make a quiz and keep track of their progress (especially basic math).
        </p>
