          Allows you to keep track of who is taking the quiz at a given time, and allows both quiz makers and quiz takers to keep track of the results of the quiz.
        </p>
        <div class="text-xl">
          <div>
            <.link href={~p"/quizzes"} class="text-xl">
              View quizzes
            </.link>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <.link href={~p"/quizzes/random/new"} class="text-xl">
              Take a random math quiz
            </.link>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
